sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant UI as UI
    participant SR as support_routes.py
    participant EH as entry_handler.py
    participant EI as evidence_ingestion.py
    participant BL as blob_storage.py
    participant AZB as Azure Blob
    participant EM as embeddings.py
    participant AZE as Azure OpenAI
    participant VS as AzureSearch VectorStore
    participant AZS as Azure AI Search

    Admin->>UI: upload evidence for case
    UI->>SR: POST /entry/case
    Note over SR: intent=CASE_INGESTION
    Note over SR: action=UPLOAD_EVIDENCE
    Note over SR: handle_case_entry() L96
    SR->>SR: _dispatch_entry_handler() L82
    SR->>EH: handle_entry(envelope) L84
    Note over EH: _handle_case_ingestion() L66
    Note over EH: action = UPLOAD_EVIDENCE L74

    EH->>EI: upload_evidence(case_id, filename, data) L36
    Note over EI: _get_evidence_store() L16
    Note over EI: AzureSearch(evidence_index_v1)

    EI->>EI: _ensure_case_exists(case_id) L68
    EI->>BL: CaseRepository.load(case_id) L102
    BL->>AZB: get_blob_client().download_blob()
    AZB-->>BL: raw JSON bytes
    BL-->>EI: case exists confirmed

    EI->>BL: upload_file("{case_id}/{filename}") L29
    BL->>AZB: upload_blob(data, overwrite=True)
    AZB-->>BL: ok
    BL-->>EI: confirmed

    EI->>EI: _extract_text(data, content_type) L75
    EI->>EI: _build_doc_id(case_id, filename) L71
    EI->>EI: build metadata{case_id, filename}

    EI->>EM: get_embeddings() L19
    Note over EM: lru_cache singleton
    Note over EM: text-embedding-3-large

    EI->>VS: _get_evidence_store() L16
    EI->>AZS: add_texts([content_text], metadatas, ids) L45
    Note over AZS: filter at search time:
    Note over AZS: case_id eq case_id
    AZE-->>AZS: embedding dim=3072
    AZS-->>EI: [doc_id]

    EI-->>EH: indexed=True
    EH-->>SR: EntryResponseEnvelope status=accepted
    SR-->>UI: EntryResponseEnvelope
    UI-->>Admin: success
